Input

"I am learning data structures"

Output

"structures"


HUMAN LOGIC (DIMAGH ME)

Sentence ko words me tod do

Ek variable rakho jo longest word yaad rakhe

Har word ka length compare karo

Jo bada ho â†’ update




class Solution {

    public static String findLongestWord(String sentence) {

        // Step 1: Split sentence into words
        String[] words = sentence.split(" ");

        // Step 2: Store longest word
        String longestWord = "";

        // Step 3: Traverse words
        for (String word : words) {

            // IMPORTANT CHECK:
            // Compare word length
            if (word.length() > longestWord.length()) {
                longestWord = word;
            }
        }

        return longestWord;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String sentence = "I am preparing for Java interviews";
        System.out.println(findLongestWord(sentence));
    }
}




## â± TIME & SPACE

- **Time Complexity:** `O(n)`  
  (n = total characters)
- **Space Complexity:** `O(n)`  
  (words array)

